Lynn Collins https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lynn_Collins 0 Viola Lynn Collins (born May 16, 1977) is an American actress. She has made television appearances in True Blood and Manhunt: Unabomber, and is recognized for her roles in films such as X-Men Origins: Wolverine and John Carter.
